        <title type="html"><![CDATA[Hunter/Healer Alpha到底是哪家的？]]></title>
        <id>https://zhichii.github.io/blog/h-alpha</id>
        <link href="https://zhichii.github.io/blog/h-alpha"/>
        <updated>2026-03-12T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[严谨地说：Hunter Alpha至少使用了MiMo的tokenizer。]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>严谨地说：<strong>Hunter Alpha至少使用了MiMo的tokenizer。</strong></p>
<p>起因是我的网友测试，用它写小说，顺便提供了输出：7.5k tokens。</p>
<p>我顺着这个思路往下走，决定利用token数量作为突破口。</p>
<p>你们也可以试试……</p>
<p>具体如下：</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="第一次">第一次<a href="https://zhichii.github.io/blog/h-alpha#%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1" class="hash-link" aria-label="第一次的直接链接" title="第一次的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>网友提供了原文（太长了不放了），我核对了一下。</p>
<p>具体数据是<strong>7.5k</strong> tokens。</p>
<table><thead><tr><th>模型</th><th>数量</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>DeepSeek V3 (等于V3.2)</td><td>6796</td></tr><tr><td>GLM 4.7</td><td>7177</td></tr><tr><td>Kimi K2.5</td><td>6483</td></tr><tr><td>MiMo V2 Flash</td><td><strong>7518</strong></td></tr><tr><td>MiniMax M2.5</td><td>6547</td></tr><tr><td>Qwen3.5</td><td>7090</td></tr><tr><td>Step 3.5 Flash</td><td>6797</td></tr></tbody></table>
<p>已经很明显了，答案就是MiMo。</p>
<p>但我为了严谨，又测试了一次。</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="第二次">第二次<a href="https://zhichii.github.io/blog/h-alpha#%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1" class="hash-link" aria-label="第二次的直接链接" title="第二次的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<div class="language-markdown codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockTitle_OeMC">Hunter Alpha回答</div><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-markdown codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">你好！很高兴为你介绍 </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">ChatGPT</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">简单来说，ChatGPT 是由人工智能研究实验室 </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">OpenAI</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain"> 开发的一个人工智能聊天机器人程序，目前是全球最知名、用户量最大的生成式 AI 应用之一。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">以下是关于它的详细介绍，分为几个关键点：</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token title important punctuation" style="color:#393A34">###</span><span class="token title important"> 1. 名字的含义</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">*</span><span class="token plain">   </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">Chat</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：聊天。代表它的交互形式是对话式的。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">*</span><span class="token plain">   </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">GPT</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">G</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">enerative </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">P</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">re-trained </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">T</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">ransformer（生成式预训练变换器）。这是驱动它的核心技术模型，它通过海量的文本数据进行训练，从而学会了理解和生成人类语言。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token title important punctuation" style="color:#393A34">###</span><span class="token title important"> 2. 它能做什么？</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">ChatGPT 的能力非常广泛，不仅限于聊天：</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">*</span><span class="token plain">   </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">知识问答</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：回答各种领域的问题（历史、科学、技术等）。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">*</span><span class="token plain">   </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">文本创作</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：写邮件、写诗、写小说、写剧本、写营销文案。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">*</span><span class="token plain">   </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">编程辅助</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：编写代码、检查代码错误、解释代码逻辑。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">*</span><span class="token plain">   </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">语言处理</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：翻译语言、总结长篇文章、润色文字、改变文风（比如用莎士比亚的风格改写句子）。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">*</span><span class="token plain">   </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">逻辑推理</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：解决数学问题、进行逻辑分析。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token title important punctuation" style="color:#393A34">###</span><span class="token title important"> 3. 核心技术与原理</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">它基于 </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">大语言模型 (Large Language Model, LLM)</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">。它并不是像传统搜索引擎那样去数据库里“查找”答案，而是根据概率预测下一个字（Token）应该是什么，从而“生成”答案。这使得它的回答通常非常流畅、自然，甚至具有一定的创造性。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token title important punctuation" style="color:#393A34">###</span><span class="token title important"> 4. 版本与发展</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">*</span><span class="token plain">   </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">早期版本</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：GPT-3.5（免费用户主要使用的版本）。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">*</span><span class="token plain">   </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">GPT-4 / GPT-4o</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：更强大的付费版本，逻辑推理能力更强，且支持</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">多模态</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">（可以看图、语音对话、生成图片等）。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">*</span><span class="token plain">   </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">GPT-o1 等新模型</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：专注于更复杂的逻辑推理和数学能力。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token title important punctuation" style="color:#393A34">###</span><span class="token title important"> 5. 局限性</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">尽管它很强大，但并非完美：</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">*</span><span class="token plain">   </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">幻觉 (Hallucinations)</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：它有时会一本正经地胡说八道，编造不存在的事实。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">*</span><span class="token plain">   </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">知识截止日期</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：虽然联网功能有所改善，但其内部知识库并非实时更新的。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">*</span><span class="token plain">   </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">缺乏真正的意识</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：它只是在模拟人类的语言模式，并不真正理解对话的含义或拥有情感。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">总的来说，ChatGPT 是人工智能发展史上的一个里程碑，它极大地降低了普通人使用 AI 的门槛，正在深刻地改变我们的工作和学习方式。</span><br></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>OpenRouter API显示<strong>571</strong> tokens。</p>
<table><thead><tr><th>模型</th><th>数量</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>GLM-4.7 (等于GLM-5)</td><td>549</td></tr><tr><td>Kimi K2.5</td><td>504</td></tr><tr><td>MiMo V2 Flash</td><td><strong>570</strong></td></tr><tr><td>MiniMax M2.5</td><td>553</td></tr><tr><td>Qwen3.5</td><td>547</td></tr></tbody></table>
<p>还是，虽然有1 token的误差。</p>
<p><em>注：我更新完transformers库之后发现DeepSeek-V3/V3.2和Step-3.5-Flash的统计有问题，就先不放了。如果你们自己测试，结果应该和我的结果一样。</em></p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="第三次">第三次<a href="https://zhichii.github.io/blog/h-alpha#%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%AC%A1" class="hash-link" aria-label="第三次的直接链接" title="第三次的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<div class="language-markdown codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockTitle_OeMC">Hunter Alpha思考</div><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-markdown codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">现在是2026年3月12日，下午2点02分（UTC+8）。我来回复用户。我会说：“你好！我是一个AI助手，可以帮助你处理各种任务。我可以搜索和查看知识库、笔记、聊天记录，以及频道消息。我还可以帮你创建和编辑笔记。你有什么需要我帮忙的吗？” 但为了更全面，我需要列出具体的功能，比如搜索知识库、查看文件、管理笔记等等。我会用中文来回复。现在，开始回复。</span><br></span></code></pre></div></div>
<div class="language-markdown codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockTitle_OeMC">Hunter Alpha回答</div><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-markdown codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">你好！今天是2026年3月12日，星期四。我是一个AI助手，可以帮助你处理多种任务。以下是我能做的一些事情：</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token title important punctuation" style="color:#393A34">###</span><span class="token title important"> 📚 知识库管理</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">-</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">搜索和查看知识库</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：我可以帮你找到并浏览你的知识库。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">-</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">搜索文件</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：在知识库中搜索特定文件。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">-</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">查看文件内容</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：获取知识库中文件的完整内容。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token title important punctuation" style="color:#393A34">###</span><span class="token title important"> 📝 笔记管理</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">-</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">搜索笔记</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：根据标题和内容查找你的笔记。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">-</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">创建笔记</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：帮你创建新的笔记。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">-</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">编辑笔记</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：更新已有笔记的内容和标题。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token title important punctuation" style="color:#393A34">###</span><span class="token title important"> 💬 聊天记录管理</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">-</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">搜索聊天</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：根据关键词查找之前的聊天对话。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">-</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">查看聊天内容</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：获取整个聊天对话的详细信息。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token title important punctuation" style="color:#393A34">###</span><span class="token title important"> 📢 频道功能</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">-</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">搜索频道</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：找到你有访问权限的频道。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">-</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">搜索频道消息</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：在频道中搜索特定消息。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">-</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">查看消息和线程</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：获取频道消息和线程回复的完整内容。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token title important punctuation" style="color:#393A34">###</span><span class="token title important"> ⏰ 时间相关工具</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token list punctuation" style="color:#393A34">-</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">获取当前时间戳</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">：我可以帮你获取当前时间或进行时间计算。</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">你有什么具体需要帮忙的吗？比如想找某个笔记、查看知识库中的文件，或者管理你的聊天记录？</span><br></span></code></pre></div></div>
